that the element is playing. The role must be consistent with the basic semantic and expectations
for the element. In particular, the <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:3;22:45" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/attributes/universalAttributes.dita">outputclass</xmlatt> attribute can be used for styling
during output processing; HTML output will typically preserve <xmlatt class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlatt " xtrc="xmlatt:4;23:71" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/attributes/universalAttributes.dita">outputclass</xmlatt> for CSS
processing.
</dd>
